[
  {
    "block_id": "demo_1",
    "items": [
      {
        "type": "cue",
        "channel": "music",
        "value": "kaidan"
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "ok you wanted a scary one - lights off"
        ],
        "effects": [
          {
            "axis": "candles",
            "delta": -10
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "most cursed ghost story in Japan — people still won't say her name on a film set without visiting her grave first"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "her name is <b>Oiwa</b>"
        ],
        "effects": [
          {
            "axis": "candles",
            "delta": -5
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Haruki",
        "messages": [
          "💀 it's midnight why did i ask"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "Edo period. Oiwa's married to a rōnin named <b>Iemon.</b>"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "broke, mean, she just had his baby, still weak from the birth"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "and he wants out — for a richer wife"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Suzune",
        "messages": [
          "I don't like where this is going."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "so they send Oiwa \"medicine\", told her it'll help her recover"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "it's poison"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "and it doesn't kill her - it disfigures her"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "half her face collapses, her hair starts coming out in fistfuls"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Ren",
        "messages": [
          "[sigh]"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "here's the image that haunts every version"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "she's at her mirror, combing her hair to look nice. and it just keeps coming"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "a whole pile of it, and underneath, the comb is wet"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "choice",
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "Not me reading this in the bath -_-"
          },
          {
            "text": "I'm under a blanket now"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "she sees her reflection"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "sees what they did"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "and with her dying breath <b>she curses Iemon's name</b>"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Tatsumi",
        "messages": [
          "And a curse spoken in the moment of dying is the kind that holds. Those are the ones that don't loosen."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "right"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "Iemon's solution:"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "he nails her body to a door"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "nails a dead servant to the other side"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "frames them as lovers"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "dumps the whole thing in the river 👍"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Haruki",
        "messages": [
          "the casual 👍 is killing me"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "laugh now - doors come back"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "wedding night with the rich girl"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "he lifts her veil - and it's Oiwa's ruined face"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "he panics, grabs his sword, cuts the demon down"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "lights up. not Oiwa."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "his new bride. he just killed her!"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "choice",
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "NO"
          },
          {
            "text": "Oh. My. God."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "that's the whole trick"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "she never chases him, she just makes him do it to himself"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "he goes to confess, sees Oiwa, swings — kills her father too"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "he goes fishing to clear his head"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "pulls something out of the water"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "it's the door"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "her face on one side, still wet"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Haruki",
        "messages": [
          "take the door back i don't want the door"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "it follows him everywhere"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "nets turn into her hair"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "lanterns into her eyes"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "his own baby looks up with her face"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "and the curse takes the whole household down with him"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "one by one, till the bloodline's just gone"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "most ghosts haunt and fade"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "Oiwa stays until there's nothing left of him to ruin"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Tatsumi",
        "messages": [
          "The play premiered in 1825. People watched it once, then began to insist the role itself was cursed — accidents, injuries, deaths, all laid at her feet."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Tatsumi",
        "messages": [
          "So even now, before any troupe stages or films it, they make the trip to her actual grave at Myōgyō-ji in Tokyo. They kneel. They ask Oiwa for her permission first."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Tatsumi",
        "messages": [
          "You can call that superstition if it comforts you. The custom has outlasted everyone who first dismissed it."
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "choice",
        "options": [
          {
            "text": "Wait, that's a REAL grave??"
          },
          {
            "text": "..."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "real grave, real temple, directors still make the trip, the ones who skip it have stories"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Haruki",
        "messages": [
          "so the curse worked so well it started haunting the people TELLING it"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "she's the only one who got out of the play"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Kou",
        "messages": [
          "sleep well 🙂"
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "message",
        "character": "Haruki",
        "messages": [
          "<b>absolutely not</b>, not after the wet comb"
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
